videos.description: Players from the Cavaliers and Grizzlies walk off the court just before their game begins to lock arms and kneel together.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Cavs, Grizzlies delay tipoff to link arms in unison) 2020/1/7 ESHEET

videos.description: Gorgui Dieng bounces a pass behind his back to De'Anthony Melton for an easy score in the paint.
videos.headline: Dieng dishes no-look dime

videos.description: Andre Drummond overpowers Jonas Valanciunas in the paint, backing him down and then finishing with a dunk through contact.
